{"type": "article", "id": 23526, "title": "带流动光影的方形桌灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133746dyhfP0cai1q8G3rs.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏方盒子一样的桌灯有一个层层变小的“洞”，它是用纸板做的，自动让光线有了层次感。从前到后滑动上面的 LED 光源时，能看到流动的光影，非常炫目。灯的造型本身具有雕塑感，流动的光影却像是现代的霓虹灯，有了另一种结合。有多位设计师参与，他们称这盏灯符合苏格拉底的名言一切都在流动中。<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/32910829/Light-Cube-Panta-Rei\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133744ioJm4SsAZyIrF6HN.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337449DoUf81C2zm4WXpN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133745rL7Aqu2SRji8IaY1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337454H7nrF38vuT5DqMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}